OOC:(I thought the original arc landed on the North American continent. But 
I could be wrong)

::Shadow Wing::

She flew next to him. She wondered about this bot. He was bigger, stronger, 
and more deadly as a fighter than she was, but for some strange reason, she 
didn't fear him.  She looked at him for a moment.  As a wolf, he was a great 
credit to his kind. She was still wary of him thought, after all, they had 
just met.  She looked at him as he asked his question.
"I'm not sure who will meet us there.  It depends on what is happeneing when 
we get there.  I have been out of contact with the arc for a while I'm not 
sure who will greet us."
She flew next to him.

From:   <cyberwolf4@p...>

Subject: Re: Neo Beast Wars

Lunarpine transformed back to wolf and followed his new freind, His
bot said to trust her as a fellow maximal, but his wolf instincts
viewed her as competition. In the wild a wolf and owl compete for the
same food. he hoped that would be different with the maximals. He
didn't want to hurt her, even to survive.
Lunarpine shook his head, trying to seperate the logic and instincts
buried in his head. To justify both he asked two questions.
"Shadow Wing where are we going and who will greet us when we
arrive?
(side question- how are we getting across the ocean from canada to
Tibet?)
